title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox Brings in the Storage Unit Items…Find Something Very Unexpected + Amy Wants to Know If It’s Okay to Show Teens an R-Rated Movie + Songs Artist Regret
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Lunchbox Brings in the Storage Unit Items…Find Something Very Unexpected + Amy Wants to Know If It’s Okay to Show Teens an R-Rated Movie + Songs Artist Regret
description:
Lunchbox visited the storage unit that he and Bobby won in the auction.  He brings in the items found and reveals how much money they can make. But there may be a catch. Amy’s daughter wanted to watch Scream at her birthday party but she debated whether it was okay or not because of it’s R-Rating. Bobby has a list of song that artist regret and why.
